    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">
      üß† PoDIChain ‚Äî Proof of Deterministic Integrity Blockchain
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Transforming pointless mining into provably useful computation.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10">
